<qti-assessment-item xmlns="http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0" xmlns:m="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance" identifier="Q52_v3" title="Q52_v3" time-dependent="false" adaptive="false" xsi:schemaLocation="http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0 https://purl.imsglobal.org/spec/qti/v3p0/schema/xsd/imsqti_asiv3p0_v1p0.xsd">
  <qti-response-declaration identifier="RESPONSE" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier">
    <qti-correct-response>
      <qti-value>ChoiceC</qti-value>
    </qti-correct-response>
  </qti-response-declaration>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="FEEDBACK" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier"/>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="SOLUTION" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier"/>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="SCORE" cardinality="single" base-type="float">
    <qti-default-value>
      <qti-value>0</qti-value>
    </qti-default-value>
  </qti-outcome-declaration>
  <qti-item-body>
    <p>
      Sea la transformación del plano
      <m:math>
        <m:mi>T</m:mi>
        <m:mo>(</m:mo>
        <m:mi>x</m:mi>
        <m:mo>,</m:mo>
        <m:mi>y</m:mi>
        <m:mo>)</m:mo>
        <m:mo>=</m:mo>
        <m:mo>(</m:mo>
        <m:mi>x</m:mi>
        <m:mo>−</m:mo>
        <m:mn>4</m:mn>
        <m:mo>,</m:mo>
        <m:mi>y</m:mi>
        <m:mo>+</m:mo>
        <m:mn>2</m:mn>
        <m:mo>)</m:mo>
      </m:math>.
      Un vértice de un cuadrilátero es el punto
      <m:math>
        <m:mi>B</m:mi>
        <m:mo>(</m:mo>
        <m:mn>3</m:mn>
        <m:mo>,</m:mo>
        <m:mo>−</m:mo>
        <m:mn>1</m:mn>
        <m:mo>)</m:mo>
      </m:math>,
      al que se aplica T.
      ¿Cuáles son las coordenadas de la imagen del punto
      <m:math>
        <m:msup>
          <m:mi>B</m:mi>
          <m:mo>&#8242;</m:mo>
        </m:msup>
      </m:math>?
    </p>
    <qti-choice-interaction response-identifier="RESPONSE" shuffle="true" max-choices="1">
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceA">
        <m:math>
          <m:mfenced open="(" close=")">
            <m:mn>7</m:mn>
            <m:mn>1</m:mn>
          </m:mfenced>
        </m:math>
        <qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceA" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. Al aplicar <m:math><m:mrow><m:mi>T</m:mi><m:mo>(</m:mo><m:mn>3</m:mn><m:mo>,</m:mo><m:mo>−</m:mo><m:mn>1</m:mn><m:mo>)</m:mo><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mo>(</m:mo><m:mn>3</m:mn><m:mo>−</m:mo><m:mn>4</m:mn><m:mo>,</m:mo><m:mo>−</m:mo><m:mn>1</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>2</m:mn><m:mo>)</m:mo><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mo>(</m:mo><m:mo>−</m:mo><m:mn>1</m:mn><m:mo>,</m:mo><m:mn>1</m:mn><m:mo>)</m:mo></m:mrow></m:math>. Por lo tanto, la imagen no es <m:math><m:mrow><m:mo>(</m:mo><m:mn>7</m:mn><m:mo>,</m:mo><m:mn>1</m:mn><m:mo>)</m:mo></m:mrow></m:math>.</qti-feedback-inline>
      </qti-simple-choice>
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceB">
        <m:math>
          <m:mfenced open="(" close=")">
            <m:mn>−1</m:mn>
            <m:mn>−3</m:mn>
          </m:mfenced>
        </m:math>
        <qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceB" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. Al aplicar <m:math><m:mrow><m:mi>T</m:mi><m:mo>(</m:mo><m:mn>3</m:mn><m:mo>,</m:mo><m:mo>−</m:mo><m:mn>1</m:mn><m:mo>)</m:mo><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mo>(</m:mo><m:mn>3</m:mn><m:mo>−</m:mo><m:mn>4</m:mn><m:mo>,</m:mo><m:mo>−</m:mo><m:mn>1</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>2</m:mn><m:mo>)</m:mo></m:mrow></m:math>, se obtiene <m:math><m:mrow><m:mo>(</m:mo><m:mo>−</m:mo><m:mn>1</m:mn><m:mo>,</m:mo><m:mn>1</m:mn><m:mo>)</m:mo></m:mrow></m:math>. Como <m:math><m:mrow><m:mo>−</m:mo><m:mn>1</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>2</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>1</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math> y no <m:math><m:mrow><m:mo>−</m:mo><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math>, esta opción no satisface el problema.</qti-feedback-inline>
      </qti-simple-choice>
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceC">
        <m:math>
          <m:mfenced open="(" close=")">
            <m:mn>−1</m:mn>
            <m:mn>1</m:mn>
          </m:mfenced>
        </m:math>
        <qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceC" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">¡Correcto! Al aplicar la transformación <m:math><m:mrow><m:mi>T</m:mi><m:mo>(</m:mo><m:mi>x</m:mi><m:mo>,</m:mo><m:mi>y</m:mi><m:mo>)</m:mo><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mo>(</m:mo><m:mi>x</m:mi><m:mo>−</m:mo><m:mn>4</m:mn><m:mo>,</m:mo><m:mi>y</m:mi><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>2</m:mn><m:mo>)</m:mo></m:mrow></m:math> al punto <m:math><m:mrow><m:mo>(</m:mo><m:mn>3</m:mn><m:mo>,</m:mo><m:mo>−</m:mo><m:mn>1</m:mn><m:mo>)</m:mo></m:mrow></m:math>, resulta <m:math><m:mrow><m:mi>T</m:mi><m:mo>(</m:mo><m:mn>3</m:mn><m:mo>,</m:mo><m:mo>−</m:mo><m:mn>1</m:mn><m:mo>)</m:mo><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mo>(</m:mo><m:mn>3</m:mn><m:mo>−</m:mo><m:mn>4</m:mn><m:mo>,</m:mo><m:mo>−</m:mo><m:mn>1</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>2</m:mn><m:mo>)</m:mo><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mo>(</m:mo><m:mo>−</m:mo><m:mn>1</m:mn><m:mo>,</m:mo><m:mn>1</m:mn><m:mo>)</m:mo></m:mrow></m:math>.</qti-feedback-inline>
      </qti-simple-choice>
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceD">
        <m:math>
          <m:mfenced open="(" close=")">
            <m:mn>−1</m:mn>
            <m:mn>5</m:mn>
          </m:mfenced>
        </m:math>
        <qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceD" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. El primer valor sí coincide, porque <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>3</m:mn><m:mo>−</m:mo><m:mn>4</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mo>−</m:mo><m:mn>1</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math>, pero el segundo debe ser <m:math><m:mrow><m:mo>−</m:mo><m:mn>1</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>2</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>1</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math> y no <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>5</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math>. Por eso la imagen no es <m:math><m:mrow><m:mo>(</m:mo><m:mo>−</m:mo><m:mn>1</m:mn><m:mo>,</m:mo><m:mn>5</m:mn><m:mo>)</m:mo></m:mrow></m:math>.</qti-feedback-inline>
      </qti-simple-choice>
    </qti-choice-interaction>
    <qti-feedback-block identifier="show" outcome-identifier="SOLUTION" show-hide="show">
      <qti-content-body>
        <p><strong>Resolución paso a paso</strong></p>
        <ol>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 1: Identificar la transformación</strong></p>
            <p>La transformación es <m:math><m:mrow><m:mi>T</m:mi><m:mo>(</m:mo><m:mi>x</m:mi><m:mo>,</m:mo><m:mi>y</m:mi><m:mo>)</m:mo><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mo>(</m:mo><m:mi>x</m:mi><m:mo>−</m:mo><m:mn>4</m:mn><m:mo>,</m:mo><m:mi>y</m:mi><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>2</m:mn><m:mo>)</m:mo></m:mrow></m:math>. Esto significa que a la coordenada <m:math><m:mrow><m:mi>x</m:mi></m:mrow></m:math> se le resta <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>4</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math> y a la coordenada <m:math><m:mrow><m:mi>y</m:mi></m:mrow></m:math> se le suma <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math>.</p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 2: Reemplazar las coordenadas del punto</strong></p>
            <p>El punto dado es <m:math><m:mrow><m:mi>B</m:mi><m:mo>(</m:mo><m:mn>3</m:mn><m:mo>,</m:mo><m:mo>−</m:mo><m:mn>1</m:mn><m:mo>)</m:mo></m:mrow></m:math>.</p>
            <p>Entonces, <m:math><m:mrow><m:mi>x</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math> y <m:math><m:mrow><m:mi>y</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mo>−</m:mo><m:mn>1</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math>.</p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 3: Calcular cada coordenada de la imagen</strong></p>
            <p>Primera coordenada: <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>3</m:mn><m:mo>−</m:mo><m:mn>4</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mo>−</m:mo><m:mn>1</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math>.</p>
            <p>Segunda coordenada: <m:math><m:mrow><m:mo>−</m:mo><m:mn>1</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>2</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>1</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math>.</p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 4: Escribir la imagen del punto</strong></p>
            <p>La imagen es <m:math><m:mrow><m:msup><m:mi>B</m:mi><m:mo>&#8242;</m:mo></m:msup><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mo>(</m:mo><m:mo>−</m:mo><m:mn>1</m:mn><m:mo>,</m:mo><m:mn>1</m:mn><m:mo>)</m:mo></m:mrow></m:math>.</p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Conclusión</strong></p>
            <p>La alternativa correcta es la <strong>C</strong>: <m:math><m:mrow><m:mo>(</m:mo><m:mo>−</m:mo><m:mn>1</m:mn><m:mo>,</m:mo><m:mn>1</m:mn><m:mo>)</m:mo></m:mrow></m:math>.</p>
          </li>
        </ol>
      </qti-content-body>
    </qti-feedback-block>
  </qti-item-body>
  <qti-response-processing>
    <qti-response-condition>
      <qti-response-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceC</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SCORE">
          <qti-base-value base-type="float">1</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceC</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceB</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceB</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceD</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceD</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else>
    </qti-response-condition>
  </qti-response-processing>
</qti-assessment-item>